Package org.pircbotx.hooks.managers

Listener Manager interface and implementations

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ListenerManager<E extends PircBotX>
    Manages everything about Listeners: adding, removing, and dispatching events to appropriate listeners.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BackgroundListenerManager
    A standard ThreadListenerManager with dedicated background threads.
    GenericListenerManager<E extends PircBotX> Deprecated
    Due to multiple new functions of PircBotX theat depend on multiple threads, this class is deprecated and is only kept for legacy reasons or special cases.
    ThreadedListenerManager<E extends PircBotX>
    Wraps a ListenerManager and adds multithreading to ThreadedListenerManager.dispatchEvent(org.pircbotx.hooks.Event).
